[
  {
    "start": 5.359,
    "end": 11.519,
    "text": "Hello everyone. Welcome back to 247 Talk",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 9.679,
    "end": 13.92,
    "text": "English. I'm Harry",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 11.519,
    "end": 16.16,
    "text": " and I'm Alex. Hello friends.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 13.92,
    "end": 19.039,
    "text": " Today we are talking about a very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 16.16,
    "end": 20.72,
    "text": "interesting situation. Speaking English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 19.039,
    "end": 23.6,
    "text": "at the airport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 20.72,
    "end": 26.08,
    "text": " Oh yes. Airports can be exciting but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 23.6,
    "end": 28.56,
    "text": "also a little scary especially if",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 26.08,
    "end": 31.119,
    "text": "English is not your first language.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 28.56,
    "end": 33.36,
    "text": " Exactly. Many English learners",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 31.119,
    "end": 37.28,
    "text": "understand English, but when they reach",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 33.36,
    "end": 40.079,
    "text": "the airport, they suddenly feel nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 37.28,
    "end": 42.719,
    "text": " Yes. Suddenly the brain says, \"Error,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 40.079,
    "end": 46.16,
    "text": "error, English not found.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 42.719,
    "end": 48.48,
    "text": " That is true. Your brain freezes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 46.16,
    "end": 50.239,
    "text": " and the airport staff speaks fast.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 48.48,
    "end": 52.239,
    "text": "People are walking everywhere.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 50.239,
    "end": 55.199,
    "text": "Announcements are happening.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.239,
    "end": 57.76,
    "text": " Yes. And you start thinking, \"What if I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 55.199,
    "end": 60.719,
    "text": "say the wrong thing? What if they don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 57.76,
    "end": 62.239,
    "text": "understand me?\" or what if I don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 60.719,
    "end": 65.36,
    "text": "understand them?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 62.239,
    "end": 67.76,
    "text": " Exactly. But today we will practice",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 65.36,
    "end": 69.2,
    "text": "simple English conversations that happen",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 67.76,
    "end": 72.159,
    "text": "at the airport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 69.2,
    "end": 74.32,
    "text": " So relax, listen carefully, and imagine",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 72.159,
    "end": 77.04,
    "text": "you're at the airport with us.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 74.32,
    "end": 79.28,
    "text": " Yes. And sometimes we will ask you a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 77.04,
    "end": 80.0,
    "text": "question so you can practice speaking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 79.28,
    "end": 80.88,
    "text": "too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.0,
    "end": 82.479,
    "text": " Ready?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.88,
    "end": 85.28,
    "text": " Let's begin.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 82.479,
    "end": 86.159,
    "text": " Harry, have you ever been nervous at an",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 85.28,
    "end": 88.56,
    "text": "airport?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 86.159,
    "end": 91.2,
    "text": " Oh, yes. The first time I traveled",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 88.56,
    "end": 92.159,
    "text": "alone, I was very nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 91.2,
    "end": 94.24,
    "text": " Really?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 92.159,
    "end": 96.079,
    "text": " Yes. I was standing at the check-in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 94.24,
    "end": 96.88,
    "text": "counter and the staff asked me a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 96.079,
    "end": 98.32,
    "text": "question.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 96.88,
    "end": 100.799,
    "text": " What did they ask?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 98.32,
    "end": 101.68,
    "text": " They asked, \"Do you have any luggage to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 100.799,
    "end": 103.92,
    "text": "check in?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 101.68,
    "end": 106.56,
    "text": " Oh, that's a common question.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 103.92,
    "end": 108.88,
    "text": " Yes, but at that moment, my brain",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 106.56,
    "end": 114.72,
    "text": "stopped working.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.88,
    "end": 118.799,
    "text": " Oh, no. I just said uh yes I have bag",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.72,
    "end": 120.479,
    "text": "big bag luggage. Yes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 118.799,
    "end": 123.92,
    "text": " That still works.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.479,
    "end": 126.479,
    "text": " Exactly. That is the first lesson today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 123.92,
    "end": 129.679,
    "text": "You don't need perfect English.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 126.479,
    "end": 131.52,
    "text": " Yes. Communication is more important",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 129.679,
    "end": 134.0,
    "text": "than perfect grammar.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 131.52,
    "end": 135.52,
    "text": " Even simple words can help you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 134.0,
    "end": 138.56,
    "text": "communicate.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 135.52,
    "end": 141.04,
    "text": "Let's imagine something. You arrive at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 138.56,
    "end": 144.48,
    "text": "the airport. You go to the check-in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 141.04,
    "end": 147.84,
    "text": "counter. The staff smiles and says,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 144.48,
    "end": 149.84,
    "text": "\"Hello, may I see your passport?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 147.84,
    "end": 152.56,
    "text": " Very common sentence.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 149.84,
    "end": 154.879,
    "text": " So, what can you say? You can say,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 152.56,
    "end": 156.239,
    "text": "\"Sure, here it is.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 154.879,
    "end": 160.319,
    "text": " Very simple.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 156.239,
    "end": 163.68,
    "text": " Or you can say, \"Here is my passport.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 160.319,
    "end": 167.36,
    "text": " Friends, try saying this sentence aloud.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 163.68,
    "end": 170.72,
    "text": " Yes. Say it with us. Here is my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 167.36,
    "end": 173.92,
    "text": "passport. One more time. Here is my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 170.72,
    "end": 174.879,
    "text": "passport. Harry, what happens after",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 173.92,
    "end": 178.4,
    "text": "check-in?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 174.879,
    "end": 180.879,
    "text": " Good question. Then the staff might ask,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 178.4,
    "end": 183.76,
    "text": "do you have any bags to check?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 180.879,
    "end": 184.959,
    "text": " And you might say, yes, I have one",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 183.76,
    "end": 187.92,
    "text": "suitcase.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 184.959,
    "end": 189.36,
    "text": " Or, I have two bags.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 187.92,
    "end": 192.239,
    "text": " Very easy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 189.36,
    "end": 193.92,
    "text": " Then they might ask, did you pack your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 192.239,
    "end": 197.04,
    "text": "bags yourself?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 193.92,
    "end": 199.68,
    "text": " Some learners get confused here. Yes,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 197.04,
    "end": 203.2,
    "text": "but it's simple. They just want to know",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 199.68,
    "end": 206.48,
    "text": "if you packed the bags. So, you can say,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.2,
    "end": 209.04,
    "text": "\"Yes, I packed them myself.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 206.48,
    "end": 212.48,
    "text": " Or simply, \"Yes, I did.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 209.04,
    "end": 215.519,
    "text": " Now, let's practice a mini conversation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 212.48,
    "end": 217.599,
    "text": "Imagine I'm the airport staff",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 215.519,
    "end": 218.48,
    "text": " and I am the traveler.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 217.599,
    "end": 219.36,
    "text": " Ready?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 218.48,
    "end": 222.319,
    "text": " Ready.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 219.36,
    "end": 225.12,
    "text": " Good morning. May I see your passport?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 222.319,
    "end": 226.319,
    "text": " Sure. Here it is. Do you have any",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 225.12,
    "end": 228.799,
    "text": "luggage?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 226.319,
    "end": 231.04,
    "text": " Yes, I have one suitcase.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 228.799,
    "end": 232.56,
    "text": " Did you pack it yourself?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 231.04,
    "end": 236.0,
    "text": " Yes, I did.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 232.56,
    "end": 238.159,
    "text": " Perfect. Please place your bag here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 236.0,
    "end": 241.36,
    "text": " Thank you. That was easy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 238.159,
    "end": 242.72,
    "text": " Yes, airport English is usually short",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 241.36,
    "end": 245.2,
    "text": "and clear.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 242.72,
    "end": 247.12,
    "text": " But Harry, what if someone does not",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.2,
    "end": 250.56,
    "text": "understand the staff?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 247.12,
    "end": 253.84,
    "text": " Very good question. Never feel shy to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 250.56,
    "end": 257.199,
    "text": "say sorry could you repeat that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 253.84,
    "end": 260.72,
    "text": " yes that sentence is very useful",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 257.199,
    "end": 262.24,
    "text": " or say could you speak slowly please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 260.72,
    "end": 265.36,
    "text": " let's practice it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 262.24,
    "end": 266.32,
    "text": " repeat after me could you repeat that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 265.36,
    "end": 269.84,
    "text": "please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 266.32,
    "end": 272.479,
    "text": " again could you repeat that please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 269.84,
    "end": 273.52,
    "text": " another common situation is security",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 272.479,
    "end": 277.199,
    "text": "check",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 273.52,
    "end": 280.08,
    "text": " ah yes the famous airport security",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 277.199,
    "end": 282.72,
    "text": " the officer might say, \"Please put your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 280.08,
    "end": 285.6,
    "text": "phone and keys in the tray.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 282.72,
    "end": 288.479,
    "text": " Or, \"Please remove your belt.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 285.6,
    "end": 290.16,
    "text": " And sometimes they say, \"Please step",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.479,
    "end": 293.84,
    "text": "through the scanner.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 290.16,
    "end": 296.08,
    "text": " Harry, the first time I heard scanner, I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 293.84,
    "end": 297.04,
    "text": "was confused.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 296.08,
    "end": 301.36,
    "text": " Really?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 297.04,
    "end": 304.24,
    "text": " Yes. I thought they said scary.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 301.36,
    "end": 307.6,
    "text": " That would be a scary airport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 304.24,
    "end": 309.6,
    "text": " Now imagine another situation. You",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 307.6,
    "end": 312.88,
    "text": "cannot find your gate.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 309.6,
    "end": 316.32,
    "text": " Oh yes, airports are huge.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 312.88,
    "end": 318.56,
    "text": " So you can ask someone, \"Excuse me,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 316.32,
    "end": 319.919,
    "text": "where is gate 12?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 318.56,
    "end": 323.6,
    "text": " Very useful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 319.919,
    "end": 325.039,
    "text": " Or say, \"Excuse me, how can I get to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 323.6,
    "end": 328.08,
    "text": "gate 12?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 325.039,
    "end": 331.12,
    "text": " Simple and polite. Let's ask the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 328.08,
    "end": 334.56,
    "text": "listeners something. You are at the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 331.12,
    "end": 337.44,
    "text": "airport and you cannot find your gate.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 334.56,
    "end": 339.28,
    "text": "What would you say? Pause for a moment",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 337.44,
    "end": 342.08,
    "text": "and try speaking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 339.28,
    "end": 343.6,
    "text": " Maybe you said, \"Excuse me, where is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 342.08,
    "end": 345.84,
    "text": "gate 12?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 343.6,
    "end": 348.24,
    "text": " Great job if you said that.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 345.84,
    "end": 349.12,
    "text": " Harry, what about ordering food at the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 348.24,
    "end": 352.56,
    "text": "airport?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 349.12,
    "end": 354.56,
    "text": " Oh, yes. Airports have many cafes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 352.56,
    "end": 355.52,
    "text": " Imagine you are tired and you want",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 354.56,
    "end": 358.479,
    "text": "coffee.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 355.52,
    "end": 359.44,
    "text": " You can say, \"Hi, can I get a coffee,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 358.479,
    "end": 361.6,
    "text": "please?\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 359.44,
    "end": 363.68,
    "text": " Or, \"I'd like a coffee.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 361.6,
    "end": 366.24,
    "text": " Very natural English.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 363.68,
    "end": 369.199,
    "text": " And maybe a sandwich.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 366.24,
    "end": 372.8,
    "text": "Yes, airports are expensive though.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 369.199,
    "end": 375.039,
    "text": " Oh yes, one sandwich costs like a small",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 372.8,
    "end": 377.68,
    "text": "treasure.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 375.039,
    "end": 379.12,
    "text": " Now, let's learn some important airport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 377.68,
    "end": 380.88,
    "text": "vocabulary.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.12,
    "end": 383.68,
    "text": " Yes, these words will help you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 380.88,
    "end": 387.6,
    "text": "understand airport conversations.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 383.68,
    "end": 389.919,
    "text": " Word number one, passport. Example,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 387.6,
    "end": 393.52,
    "text": "please show your passport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 389.919,
    "end": 395.44,
    "text": " Word number two, boarding pass. Example,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 393.52,
    "end": 399.44,
    "text": "here is your boarding pass.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 395.44,
    "end": 401.919,
    "text": " Word number three, luggage. Example, I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 399.44,
    "end": 405.759,
    "text": "have two pieces of luggage.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 401.919,
    "end": 408.479,
    "text": " Word number four, gate. Example, our",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 405.759,
    "end": 412.319,
    "text": "flight leaves from gate 15.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 408.479,
    "end": 414.8,
    "text": " Word number five, security. Example,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 412.319,
    "end": 418.56,
    "text": "please go through security.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 414.8,
    "end": 420.8,
    "text": " Word number six, flight. Example, my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 418.56,
    "end": 424.639,
    "text": "flight is at 700 p.m.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 420.8,
    "end": 426.4,
    "text": " Word number seven, delay. Example, the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 424.639,
    "end": 429.12,
    "text": "flight is delayed.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 426.4,
    "end": 431.759,
    "text": " Oh, no. Nobody likes delays.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 429.12,
    "end": 435.199,
    "text": " Yes, but they happen sometimes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 431.759,
    "end": 438.08,
    "text": " Word number eight, departure. Example,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 435.199,
    "end": 441.84,
    "text": "the departure time is 9:00 a.m.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 438.08,
    "end": 444.639,
    "text": " Word number nine, arrival. Example, the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 441.84,
    "end": 448.319,
    "text": "arrival time is 11:00 a.m.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 444.639,
    "end": 450.72,
    "text": " Word number 10, terminal. Example, the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 448.319,
    "end": 454.16,
    "text": "flight leaves from terminal 2.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 450.72,
    "end": 455.599,
    "text": " Try repeating these words after us.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 454.16,
    "end": 457.199,
    "text": "Passport,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 455.599,
    "end": 458.56,
    "text": " boarding pass,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 457.199,
    "end": 459.759,
    "text": " luggage,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 458.56,
    "end": 461.199,
    "text": " gate,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 459.759,
    "end": 462.4,
    "text": " security,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.199,
    "end": 465.44,
    "text": " flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 462.4,
    "end": 469.039,
    "text": " Remember something important. Confidence",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 465.44,
    "end": 472.96,
    "text": "is more important than perfect English.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 469.039,
    "end": 474.0,
    "text": " Yes. Speak slowly, use simple words, and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 472.96,
    "end": 476.639,
    "text": "smile.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 474.0,
    "end": 479.12,
    "text": " People at airports talk to travelers",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 476.639,
    "end": 480.4,
    "text": "every day. They are used to different",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 479.12,
    "end": 482.16,
    "text": "accents.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 480.4,
    "end": 484.96,
    "text": " So, don't panic.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 482.16,
    "end": 486.16,
    "text": " Exactly. If you forget a word, just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 484.96,
    "end": 489.039,
    "text": "explain.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 486.16,
    "end": 490.08,
    "text": " For example, the place where the plane",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 489.039,
    "end": 492.879,
    "text": "leaves.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 490.08,
    "end": 493.84,
    "text": " And the person might say, \"Oh, the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 492.879,
    "end": 497.28,
    "text": "gate.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 493.84,
    "end": 500.24,
    "text": " Yes, communication works. Before we",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 497.28,
    "end": 501.599,
    "text": "finish, let's do one last mini",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 500.24,
    "end": 502.56,
    "text": "conversation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 501.599,
    "end": 505.68,
    "text": " Okay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 502.56,
    "end": 508.479,
    "text": " Excuse me. Where is gate 8?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 505.68,
    "end": 509.44,
    "text": " Go straight and turn left.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 508.479,
    "end": 511.84,
    "text": " Thank you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 509.44,
    "end": 512.88,
    "text": " You're welcome. Have a nice flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 511.84,
    "end": 515.2,
    "text": " Thank you,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 512.88,
    "end": 516.56,
    "text": " friends. If you are learning English,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 515.2,
    "end": 519.2,
    "text": "remember something.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 516.56,
    "end": 521.2,
    "text": " Every conversation is practice.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 519.2,
    "end": 522.159,
    "text": " Even small conversations",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 521.2,
    "end": 523.039,
    "text": " at a cafe,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 522.159,
    "end": 525.44,
    "text": " at a shop,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 523.039,
    "end": 527.2,
    "text": " or at the airport. And don't forget to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 525.44,
    "end": 530.24,
    "text": "practice speaking out loud.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 527.2,
    "end": 531.68,
    "text": " Yes, listening is good, but speaking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 530.24,
    "end": 534.399,
    "text": "makes you confident.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 531.68,
    "end": 536.48,
    "text": " We hope today's conversation helps you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 534.399,
    "end": 538.72,
    "text": "feel more confident at the airport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 536.48,
    "end": 540.08,
    "text": " and helps you speak English a little",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 538.72,
    "end": 541.76,
    "text": "more everyday.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.08,
    "end": 543.36,
    "text": " If you enjoyed this episode,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 541.76,
    "end": 546.08,
    "text": " please like the video.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 543.36,
    "end": 547.519,
    "text": " Subscribe to 247 Talk English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 546.08,
    "end": 550.399,
    "text": " and write a comment.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 547.519,
    "end": 551.2,
    "text": " Tell us, have you ever spoken English at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 550.399,
    "end": 554.16,
    "text": "an airport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 551.2,
    "end": 555.44,
    "text": " or where do you want to travel? We would",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 554.16,
    "end": 556.56,
    "text": "love to hear from you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 555.44,
    "end": 557.839,
    "text": " Thank you for listening.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 556.56,
    "end": 558.8,
    "text": " Keep practicing,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 557.839,
    "end": 560.88,
    "text": " keep speaking,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 558.8,
    "end": 563.279,
    "text": " and we will see you in the next episode",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
